{"tid":112824,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大把要好好把握今轉牛氣沖天既市, 玩完後有排食谷種","createTime":"2017-02-08T12:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T17:34:48.000Z","uid":34286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7ab3266403049d07067f92e65395c33483f9d19","tid":112824,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T12:43:07.000Z","msg":"我個高手FD一早同我講, 大戶會新年後做野炒上<br />\n今年個市先高後低, 呢轉炒完就收皮<br />\n初時我唔信, 而家事實擺在眼前<br />\n<br />\n可能大家質疑我個高高高手fd<br />\n佢戰績係好似13年開始炒, 20萬炒到而家估計&gt;500萬身家<br />\n<br />\n而家事實擺在眼前<br />\nd股, 45度向上/一支大陽燭破頂/圓底爆上<br />\n今日388核爆, 2628又創新高<br />\n其他有潛質既2382, 175呢d似領頭羊走勢<br />\n3323似谷底回升, 今日又核爆<br />\n<br />\n今日好多股都爆升, 牛氣沖天<br />\n但相信今年只係炒呢一浸, 短則1-2個月, 長則都應該唔過半年<br />\n大家要好好把握今次機會了<br />\nMiss左之後要食谷種了"},{"pid":"4269a59d45a6b2504c74fa850b821f7cc45b9a87","tid":112824,"uid":68821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T12:46:05.000Z","msg":"樂觀SIR 返黎了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cced13618daa1abff39b5f6b9de7d915a9ae5239","tid":112824,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T12:46:33.000Z","msg":"樂觀sir你個兩個高手fd又出山呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d58dd860d35da1c6ca19de32a9f5da880877fd1","tid":112824,"uid":62881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T12:58:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樂觀sir你個兩個高手fd又出山呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n珍惜樂觀Sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"